{"tid":791631,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳帆：高鐵是希望提供便利並非只為回本","createTime":"2018-08-24T02:59:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-24T05:58:51.000Z","uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":67,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"30028ebbb2aa5691f6acdd21d4b0c11236776813","tid":791631,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T02:59:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/24/105840_721c9cb1078155846b68575215f3393e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F24%2F105840_721c9cb1078155846b68575215f3393e.png&h=a4d288a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府昨日正式宣佈廣深港高鐵香港段9月23日通車，但最初的承諾全面走數，預測乘客量縮水至每天只有約8萬人，大幅減少近三成，而經濟效益也由4%降至2%。運輸及房屋局局長陳帆今早出席電台節目時承認估算較保守，但認為上座率會逐步上升，長遠對財務和持續發展都有益。<br />\n<br />\n陳帆指出估算相對保守，但認為最重要將實際操作預期讓公眾了解，又認為旅客需時適應以高鐵跨境的出行方式，相信長遠上座率會逐步上升，對於由香港至廣州只需47分鐘的列車每天只有3班，其餘九成班次行車時間均逾1小時。陳帆解釋當局在持續發展和方便客人取得平衡，又認為停站時間不算太長，當上座率達到某個百分率，便會與內地研究增加直通班次。<br />\n<br />\n政府、港鐵及九鐵三方昨簽訂4項重要協議。其中《服務經營權補充協議》訂明，九鐵公司把授予港鐵公司的經營權訂為10年，而合約年期反映日後高鐵香港段的硬件維修保養，可能要由政府負責，變相可能由納稅人補貼。陳帆表示港鐵是上市公司，需要向股東負責，如果安排令港鐵「穩蝕」，港鐵只會不願參與營運。他又指建造高鐵希望為市民提供便利，並非只為回本，而是為了社會經濟效益和整體發展。"},{"pid":"9a35dbaaeae4c704bfefb1b1569cceaae03fce12","tid":791631,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T02:59:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180824/58600991\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180824%2F58600991&d=nId%2B%2FjsKSSECTGJHDkk0py7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=4cfecbcf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180824%2F58600991&h=dcc14591\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180824/58600991</a>"},{"pid":"1f3bf1bfb1fb74d95b263538ab35e3fa44b4db0e","tid":791631,"uid":41116,"like":43,"dislike":2,"score":41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T03:02:27.000Z","msg":"高鐵係政治工程<br />\n梗係唔洗收回<br />\n你班賣港賊"},{"pid":"3694b64375eacf71e0a823e1fb988a4e9bdad9d7","tid":791631,"uid":38552,"like":59,"dislike":1,"score":58,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T03:06:28.000Z","msg":"一年後：高鐵只希望提供建造業就業機會並非用作使用。"},{"pid":"1e27331d5f9b79063d76d4b0c758294ef4a0afb8","tid":791631,"uid":181868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T03:07:42.000Z","msg":"今天我～<br />\n打倒昨天的我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c9b677f9b288bab12dc28f895485dc2da5fff01","tid":791631,"uid":198175,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T03:08:33.000Z","msg":"提供上貢抽水的便利, 起嗰時超晒支要畀成千億, 以後仲要蝕本補貼幾十年, 回扣抽水豆腐渣當然少不了, 這也是一種便利, 當然不可能回本啦, 咁誠實, 抵讚!"},{"pid":"20a39c67193a5bc00b1a98bd427e71d981ba1094","tid":791631,"uid":33864,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T03:09:09.000Z","msg":"搞手只求打個和<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5eba3201541619f5cdbff77bc92218a618ea936b","tid":791631,"uid":18604,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T03:10:10.000Z","msg":"唔求回本<br />\n咁地鐵唔好加價得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f1eef9e5b77c0022d1a86306ca10c6f7fa64750","tid":791631,"uid":192618,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T03:12:48.000Z","msg":"南水北調, 不嬲都係國策黎架啦, 你地冇做錯到!"},{"pid":"9d1f6d8b4006e7126013aff783108e7e742b9069","tid":791631,"uid":196321,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T03:14:04.000Z","msg":"搞唔到咪當高速過山車變機動遊戲收10蚊玩一次"},{"pid":"5961187ab28a9dd4a30cd7a70fcd30c7a9206b82","tid":791631,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T03:14:59.000Z","m